content:
Workout Video:


Warmup:
-20 Dislocations

-3 Sets of:
10 Jump Squats
10 Pushups
10 Good mornings

-10 Rollups

Strength:
Weighted Bulgarian Split Squat
12-12-12-12-12 (6 each leg)
20 Hollow Rocks after each set
*Rest 2min

Metcon:
For time:
5 Rounds of:
20 Russian Swings (kb/db/backpack)
20 Goblet Squats

Rest 5min then,

5 Rounds of:
10 Strict Door Pullups / 20 Sheet Rows
10 Jacksons
